Package: fplot
Type: Package
Title: Formlua Based Plotting
Version: 0.0
Date: 2015-05-15
Author: Randall Pruim <rpruim@calvin.edu>, Daniel Kaplan <dtkaplan@macalester.edu>
Maintainer: Randall Pruim <rpruim@calvin.edu>
Description: This package provides a unified formula-based interface to plotting
    routines in the ggplot2 and lattice packages.
Depends: R (>= 3.0)
License: GPL (>=2)
LazyLoad: yes
LazyData: yes
Imports: 
    ggplot2,
    lattice,
    mosaic
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    dplyr,
    formula.tools,
    mosaicData
